the techniques I tried to experiment on this one, were:
  • low-angle sketching 4 scratchy lines (bottom of right face side, and rays beside left face side)
  • using negative space in black objects to convey white objects (rays under right face side)
  • super close horizontal lines (left face side)
  • conveying reflective surfaces (left eye)
